WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.459 --> 00:00:04.860
We want you to participate virtually
in the World Economic Forum’s Summer

00:00:04.860 --> 00:00:09.260
Davos in China this September.
The theme of the meeting is "Driving Growth

00:00:09.260 --> 00:00:13.290
through Sustainability".
At the Annual Meeting of the New Champions

00:00:13.290 --> 00:00:17.789
held in Tianjin we want to know about YOUR
solutions for sustainability.

00:00:17.789 --> 00:00:24.019
How can we manage resources more efficiently?
How can we increase energy efficiency?

00:00:24.019 --> 00:00:30.419
How can we lower carbon emissions?
How can we rebuild basic infrastructure?

00:00:30.419 --> 00:00:33.609
These are just a few questions that we want
YOU to help answer.

00:00:33.609 --> 00:00:39.629
All innovative ideas are welcome because driving
growth through sustainability is fundamental

00:00:39.629 --> 00:00:44.929
for global, national and business competitiveness
in the 21st century.

00:00:44.929 --> 00:00:50.199
Ready to pitch? Upload your pitch using a
visually stimulating presentation that is

00:00:50.199 --> 00:00:56.489
no longer than 2 minutes to YouTube.com/Davos.
The more visual, the better!

00:00:56.489 --> 00:01:00.039
Don’t forget to vote for your favourite
presentation too.

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:03.230
The best entry will be shown to some of the
most powerful and influential people in the

00:01:03.230 --> 00:01:08.159
world - including presidents and business
leaders - at our Summer Davos in China.

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:11.830
Go to YouTube.com/Davos to join the conversation.

